Tera Patrick https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tera_Patrick 0 Tera Patrick (born Linda Ann Hopkins July 25, 1976) is the stage name of an American pornographic actress and model. Patrick is the Penthouse Pet of the Month for February 2000 and is an inductee for the NightMoves, AVN and XRCO Halls of Fame.
